  <preparation><![CDATA[For all:  Cut tomatoes lengthwise and discard seeds.  Stuff about 4 hours before serving.   Cover & refrigerate.

Cheese & Shrimp:  mix cheese, catsup and dill, stuff tomatoes and top with shrimp.

Guacamole:  mix ingredients together, stuff and top with crisp bacon.

Alternate method:  Fill tomatoes with sauce of chopped onion, cream cheese, sour cream and black pepper.  Top with a bit of parsley.]]></preparation>
